# Bee Kiss Premium E-Commerce Website

## Overview
I have successfully built a premium, luxurious e-commerce experience for the forest honey brand, **Bee Kiss**. The website leverages a pure Vanilla HTML/CSS/JS stack ensuring fast load times, excellent SEO structure, and high-performance smooth animations. 

## Key Achievements & Features
- **Design System & Aesthetics**: Implemented a sophisticated dark forest green (`#0F2E1D`), honey gold (`#D4A017`), and cream white palette, beautifully paired with Playfair Display headings and Inter body text.
- **AI Asset Generation**: Created bespoke, high-quality 8K imagery for the Wayanad forest hero background, authentic honey gatherer story section, and luxury product packaging mockups.
- **Frontend Interactivity**: Fully functional shopping cart utilizing `localStorage` to preserve state across page reloads. The cart includes a smooth slide-out UI and handles quantity modifications dynamically.
- **Smooth Animations**: Integrated Intersection Observer to trigger elegant "fade-up" and "fade-in" animations as sections scroll into view, reinforcing the premium feel.
- **Checkout Flow**: Designed a secure checkout page mock which simulates a Razorpay transaction, calculating subtotal and static shipping costs before displaying a success completion state.
- **Responsive & SEO**: The semantic HTML5 structure is fully responsive from mobile to wide desktop screens.

## Project Structure
All files were generated in the requested location:
- `C:\Users\fresh\.gemini\antigravity\scratch\beekiss\`
  - `index.html` - The main one-page luxurious store interface.
  - `checkout.html` - The secure checkout process UI.
  - `css/styles.css` - Custom vanilla CSS styling and design tokens.
  - `js/app.js` - Core cart state logic, homepage interactions, and scroll animations.
  - `js/checkout.js` - Logic dedicated to rendering the cart summary and mock payment flow on the checkout page.
  - `images/` - Contains the four AI generated premium assets.

